      • pumpDiesel

        public void pumpDiesel​(long amount)
                throws PumpException,
                       TankException
        Removes specified amount of gas from the DieselTank
        Parameters:
        amount - amount of gas in gallons to remove
        Throws:
        PumpException - Exception thrown if there is problem when pumping gas.
        TankException - Exception thrown if there is low gas or out of gas within tank.

      • pumpMidGrade

        public void pumpMidGrade​(long amount)
                  throws PumpException,
                         TankException
        Removes specified amount of gas from the Premium and Unleaded Tanks.
        Parameters:
        amount - amount of gas in gallons to remove (half to premium, half to unleaded tanks)
        Throws:
